            <div class="container-fluid py-2"> 
                <h3 class="display-5">'80-86 Ladies</h3> 
                <p class="lead col-md-12" style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Reunited, revived… and occasionally hot-flushed!</em></strong> It started with Mummy Norah’s “Banange, let’s have our own group - just the ladies!” And just like that, the spin-off was born. This lively bunch of 50+ women is juggling work, relationships, grown children, and hot flashes that could start a small fire. Once in a while we get cheeky, share heartfelt rants, wellness tips and parenting hacks, and swap hilarious adulting stories. </p>
                <p class="lead col-md-12" style="text-align: justify;"> This lively bunch of 50+ women is juggling work, relationships, grown children, and hot flashes that could start a small fire. Once in a while we get cheeky, share heartfelt rants, wellness tips and parenting hacks, and swap hilarious adulting stories. </p>          
            </div>                         
