                <h3 class="display-5">'80-86 Ladies cont...</h3>
                <p class="lead col-md-12" style="text-align: justify;">And then there are the moments when we get raw. Suddenly, the polite pleasantries vanish, replaced by frustration and pain… and just like that, the chat transforms into a therapy session and a safe space all at once.</p>                 
                <p class="lead col-md-12" style="text-align: justify;">The Ladies "Brunch" on 31 May 2025, hosted by our lovely headgirl, was well-attended . Amid elegant sips and tiny bites, the conversation got progressively unfiltered, the laughter long and loud… Through this bond we remind ourselves that true sisterhood doesn’t age - it just gets louder, hotter, and a little more honest.</p>
                <h5 class="lead fw-bold"><em>by Carol Kibukamusoke</em></h5>  
